分都應驗到橋段"},{"pid":"e4349c79d3bd451e94e71e51851a8e7f07ce7875","tid":2387624,"uid":20641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"武肺呢一仗可以話大勝 打到西方散哂<br />\n嚐到甜頭 中共未來仲唔全力發展化武咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bab577b329d5b27f3396a77f39ae9e07ea3e0c","tid":2387624,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"武肺2.0"}]}